===Etymology===
From {{inh|de|gmh|sameztac|sameztac, samztac}}, from {{inh|de|goh|sambaztag||Sabbath day}}, from {{der|de|got|*𐍃𐌰𐌼𐌱𐌰𐍄𐍉}}, an alteration (possibly dialectal) of earlier, Biblical {{m|got|𐍃𐌰𐌱𐌱𐌰𐍄𐍉}}. The altered Gothic form derives from {{der|de|gkm|*σάμβατον||Sabbath}}. Compare {{cog|fr|samedi}}, {{cog|fro|sambedi}}, {{cog|rm|somda}}, {{cog|ro|sâmbătă}}, {{cog|hu|szombat}}, {{cog|cu|сѫбота}}.

